snippet.title: Target Earth Sega Genesis HD Full Run (Long Play)
snippet.description:
See a new long play here!! https://youtu.be/ictYn-hFaSU

Here is a Full Run of Target Earth for the Sega Genesis...
The is game is also called Assault Suits Leynos in Japan and its not censored. It also has some different dialog. (Cybernator aka Assault Suits Valken is the prequel to Target Earth aka Assault Suits Leynos and also has a similar trick on the first stage FYI) 
If you are wondering why I didn't shoot anything on the first stage except for the warship. A 2800 first stage score all weapons trick was performed...(Which is why all weapons are present starting on the second stage)

Some save states were used to make this video. Saves were used at the end of stages. Play-through was real though.
